---

<section class="lav-event_index">
  <div class="lav-event_inner">
    <div class="lav-event_index_text">
      <h1>HAR DU IDEER TIL ET NYT HEADSPACE EVENT?</h1>
      <p>Vi arbejder hele tiden på at finde nye måder at engagere flere mennesker i at støtte unges trivsel.</p>
      <p>Har du en idé til et fremtidigt Headspace-event? Udfyld formularen og send den afsted til os — sammen skaber vi fællesskaber, hvor unge bliver set, hørt og støttet.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="lav-event_form-wrap">
      <div class="lav-event_form">
        <form>
          <fieldset>
            <legend>Personlige Oplysninger</legend>

            <label for="name">Navn</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name" />

            <label for="phone">Telefon nummer</label>
            <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" />

            <label for="email">Gmail</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email" />
          </fieldset>

          <fieldset>
            <legend>Dine Ideer</legend>

            <label for="about">Skriv om dine ideer til et event! Giv gerne ideer til tid, sted, og indhold.</label>
            <textarea id="about" name="about"></textarea>
          </fieldset>

          <button type="submit">send dit event!</button>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ── Section shell ── */
  .lav-event_index {
    width: 100%;
    background-color: #d8cde6;
    padding: 80px 32px;
  }

  /* ── Inner container — mirrors SoMe's .container ── */
  .lav-event_inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
    display: flex;
  }

  /* ── Left: text ── */
  .lav-event_index_text h1 {
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #7db742;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .lav-event_index_text p {
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }

  /* ── Right: form wrap — mirrors SoMe's .video-card ── */
  .lav-event_form-wrap {
    max-width: 75%;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  /* ── Form card ── */
  .lav-event_form {
    background: #ffffff;
    border: 4px solid #5e357c;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    width: 100%;
  }

  /* Fieldset */
  .lav-event_form fieldset {
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .lav-event_form legend {
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: #5e357c;
  }

  /* Labels */
  .lav-event_form label {
    display: block;
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 3px;
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  /* Inputs + textarea */
  .lav-event_form input,
  .lav-event_form textarea {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    border: 1.5px solid #000000;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    background: #ffffff;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    outline: none;
    transition: border-color 0.15s;
  }

  .lav-event_form input:focus,
  .lav-event_form textarea:focus {
    border-color: #5e357c;
  }

  .lav-event_form textarea {
    height: 70px;
    resize: none;
  }

  /* Submit button */
  .lav-event_form button {
    width: 100%;
    background: #cbbddd;
    color: #5e357c;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-family: "Agrandir", sans-serif;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    margin-top: 4px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .lav-event_form button:hover {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .lav-event_inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .lav-event_form-wrap {
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
